This paper proposes a crossover operator for evolutionary algorithms with real values, which is relevant to the fields of neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses statistical analysis of the results, which is relevant to the field of systems and control (cs.SY) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
